	<p><b>Quick Start:</b></p>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
	<p>First, try to find a Provider record using one or more of the following search techniques:</p>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
	<ol id="font81">
	  <li>Search by Individual or Facility Name and State. If search is too broad, or too many records are returned, try adding a City. You can also use a partial first name.<br /><br /></li>
	  <li>Search by NPI Number<br /><br/></li>
	  <li>Search by Name, Address, City and State.<br /><br/></li>
	  <li>Search by Company Name and Tax ID (FEIN).<br /><br/></li>
	  <li>Search by Name and SSN.<br /><br/></li>
	  <li>Search by Name, License Number and State.<br /><br/></li>
	</ol>
